{"title":"Invert the case of letters in the text","description":"Invert the case of alphabetic characters in the text, all lowercase letters are converted to uppercase and vice versa - all uppercase letters are converted to lowercase","content":"## Inverting letters in the text\r\nThis tool allows you to invert the case of alphabetic characters in the text: all lowercase letters are converted to uppercase and vice versa - all uppercase letters are converted to lowercase.\r\nThis application allows you to select the section of text that you want to invert.\n\n You can also familiarize yourself with other functionality of this online [text editor](/en/editor)."}